  <has_model_selection_observations rdf:resource="#modelselectionobservation1"/>
  <description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Olist migration KMDS workflow with cleaned customer/order data, featurization for SP 2017 weekly product affinity, unsupervised spectral clustering, and knowledge graph export. Key components: dd-parser-cleaner metadata profiling and cleaning; featurization pipeline from featurizer_config.yaml; spectral coclustering modeling from modeling_config.yaml; and KMDS knowledge graph generation via kmds-data-helper. Data inputs include Olist raw order, order item, customer, payment, review, seller, and geolocation datasets. Prepared outputs include SP_2017 weekly revenue/product matrices and customer clean CSV artifacts. Generated artifacts ingested into KMDS: output/full_service_report.json, documents/*.md, agent_documents/*.md, notebooks/*.ipynb summaries, and resulting project graph data/kmds/project_knowledge_graph.xml.</description>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

